quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonannde gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa O √Īaawiray hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Ďaawoore Makko ngal, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Anndu…óo"
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an hi…óa e hoore Goonga …ďannguka kan"
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa may…ďe …ďen, a nanintaa faa…óu…ďe …ďen noddaandu ndun si …ďe …óuurnike …ďe huccitii"
  27,81,An a wonaali fewnoowo bum…ďe …ďen e gaayi majjere ma…ď…ďe nden. A nanintaa si wanaa …ďen gom…óin…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ďe ko …ďe jebbilii…ďe
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow ma…ď…ďe, Men yaltinana …ďe daabewa immorde ka leydi himba haalana …ďe wonnde yim…ďe …ďen laatike …ďe yananaaka Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  27,83,E √Īalnde Men moo…ďoyta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaa…ďe e …ďen fennoo…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ďe hi…ďe soggee
  27,84,"Haa si …ďe arii, O Daala: \"Eyoo, on fenniino Aayeeje Am …óen, hara on hu…ďindoraali …ói ganndal. Kaa ko hon…óum won…óon e gollude"
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e ma…ď…ďe sabu ko …ďe too√Īi kon, kam…ďe …ďe wowlataa"
  27,86,"Enee, hara …ďe yi'aali, Menen Men wa…óii jemma on fii yo …ďe dee∆īu e maako, e √Īalorma on yi'ir…óo? Pellet, wonii e …óum Aayeeje wonannde yim…ďe gom…óinoo…ďe …ďen"
  27,87,"E √Ďalnde wuttoytee ka alaadu, …óen∆īoo …ďen wonu…ďe ka kammuuli e …ďen wonu…ďe ka leydi, si wanaa …ďen …ďe Alla muuyi, gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe aray e Makko hara ko …ďe hoykinii…ďe"
  27,88,"Hi…óa tina pelle …óen, sikka ko …óe fenndii…óe, hara le kannje hi…óe wuloo wulagol duule …óen, …óum ko kuugal Alla, On Ňčar…óin…óo kala huunde, pellet, Kanko ko O Humpitii…óo ko golloton kon"
